                         Transparent Pricing
                    </span>
                    <h2 class="cs-title">Landscape Maintenance Pricing in Las Cruces</h2>
                    <p class="cs-text">Landscape maintenance pricing depends on the property, not a flat menu. A small desert front yard on a monthly plan looks very different from a half-acre estate with turf, trees, and drip irrigation. Here is how we figure out the price for your property.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="cs-price-body">
                    <div class="cs-price-col">
                        <h3 class="cs-price-subtitle">Your Quote Is Built Around:</h3>
                        <ul class="cs-bullets">
                            <li>Property size (square footage of maintained area)</li>
                            <li>Visit frequency (weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly)</li>
                            <li>Number and type of plants that need regular care</li>
                            <li>Size and complexity of the irrigation system</li>
                            <li>Turf vs xeriscape ratio (turf takes more weekly work)</li>
                            <li>One-time setup work if the yard needs a reset visit</li>
                            <li>Special requests: pet-safe products, organic-only options, gated entry scheduling</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cs-price-col">
                        <h3 class="cs-price-subtitle">Free On-Site Estimates</h3>
                        <p class="cs-price-para">Every quote starts with a free property walk. We look at the yard, talk through what you want, and send you a written plan with clear pricing before any work starts. No surprise fees, no auto-renewals, no quotes over the phone based on a guess.</p>
                        <h3 class="cs-price-subtitle">Predictable Monthly Billing</h3>
                        <p class="cs-price-para">Recurring plans are billed monthly, not per visit. That keeps landscape maintenance cost predictable for budgeting and avoids sticker shock after a heavy growth month. Affordable landscape maintenance is not about cutting corners, it is about matching the plan to the property so you are not paying for work your yard does not need.</p>
                        <h3 class="cs-price-subtitle">HOA and Commercial Quotes</h3>
                        <p class="cs-price-para">Commercial landscape maintenance pricing is built from the property walk and can be delivered as line-item bids to match your RFP format. Monthly landscape maintenance cost for multi-property contracts is structured around a single point of contact and consolidated billing.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
